<h3 id="important-keyboard-shortcuts">Important Keyboard Shortcuts</h3>

<p>These keyboard shortcuts should be committed to memory. Theyâ€™ll help you with this assignment and all the rest of your Photoshop work, especially when youâ€™re working with layer masks.</p>

<p>D: Set foreground &amp; background swatches to default colours, black &amp; white.</p>

<p>X: Switch focus of foreground/background colours.</p>

<p>âŒ˜-Delete: Fill with background colour.</p>

<p>Option-Delete: Fill with foreground colour.</p>

<p>B: Brush Tool. Right-click with Brush tool for controls.</p>

